title: Football | Top 10 teams in South Hampton Roads
text:
This list was last updated on Sept. 30, 2015. The Virginian-Pilot's South Hampton Roads high school football poll, as voted upon by Pilot football staffers Jami Frankenberry, Larry Rubama, Lee Tolliver, Ray Nimmo, Brian Saunders, Kyle Hampson and John Streit. (first-place votes in parentheses).
Dropped out: Grassfield (3-1).
Also receiving votes: Grassfield 4.
